t. This year he and Blunt will appear in <i>The Smashing Machine</i> , a biopic of legendary MMA fighter Mark Kerr directed by <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/uncut-gems-review-adam-sandler-2595412"><i>Uncut Gems</i></a> &#39; Benny Safdie – a role that <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/dwayne-johnson-wants-to-do-more-dramatic-work-on-films-that-matter-3566744">signals Johnson&#39;s intention to move into more dramatic work</a> .</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/martin-scorsese-dwayne-johnson-team-up-shocks-fans-something-i-never-thought-would-happen-3840148">Martin Scorsese and Dwayne Johnson team-up shocks fans: “Something I never thought would happen”</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
